      propertyPath: journalFullText
      value: After trekking through the underground, I have finally reached the surface.
        It looks like there might be something buried beneath that wood over there,
        in the shade. It would be ideal if there was some slime mold over there,
        but I can't see any... maybe if I could use my fan tool to blow some slime
        mold spores from this side over to the other side?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
